This paper deals with data storage and retrieval in OLAP systems, which is a topic closely related to database management (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses optimization techniques for efficient data retrieval, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to optimize the storage mechanism, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
